      "$description": "Custom color — an app-specific hue outside the core palette: positive/success accent, distinct from secondary/tertiary so it reads unambiguously as 'you're owed'. Generated algorithmically (constant hue/chroma across every tone) from the hue/chroma of the previous hand-authored seed (#1f8f6a), so every stop is a real, verified HCT tone rather than a hand-picked approximation.",
      "0": { "$value": "#000000" },
      "10": { "$value": "#002115" },
      "20": { "$value": "#003827" },
      "30": { "$value": "#00513a" },
      "40": { "$value": "#006c4d" },
